author: felicity
msg: autolearning will now only take place with scoresets 0 and 1.  if we're
using 2 or 3, the autolearn code will revert to 0 or 1 and recompute
the score, then check about autolearning.  this gives us consistency in
autolearning on the same scoresets all the time.
